headline: Q1 Industrial Packaging Earnings: Ball (NYSE:BALL) Impresses
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Ball (NYSE:BALL) and the rest of the industrial packaging stocks fared in Q1.
